# Demo: Subagent Spawning
# Shows spawning explore and task subagents

Output docs/images/demo-subagents.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Padding 20

Type "jdai --new --dangerously-skip-permissions"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "Use an explore agent to analyze the project structure and explain what this codebase does"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 20s

Screenshot docs/images/demo-subagents.png
Sleep 2s
